{"type": "article", "id": 31414, "title": "你见过竹荪造型的灯吗？｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2016-08-24T23:11:22Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 31947, "name": "JiyounKim Studio"}, {"id": 31948, "name": "mob"}, {"id": 31949, "name": "易承桃"}, {"id": 31950, "name": "Damien Gernay"}, {"id": 31951, "name": "Lindsey Nelson"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 8, "praise_count": 106, "image": "img/article/article_show/201608242329100nCrG73W2IXwbUJt.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>Pencil Note by 易承桃</h3><p>设计师<a href=\"http://www.chengtaoyi.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">易承桃</a>随身会携带笔记本和木质铅笔，当他发现不少人也会因为铅笔不能像钢笔或者是圆珠笔那样的夹在笔记本上而感到困扰时，一个将两者结合在一起的想法由此而生。他在这款名为 Pencil Note 的笔记本封面上设计了一个凹槽，可以容纳几乎所有类型的木质铅笔。随着铅笔在使用过程中慢慢削短或者替换成新的一支，凹槽看上去就像是游戏中代表生命值的血条一样不断变化。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160824233254CjWEQB4ma9pfgi6s.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.646699\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160824233254D1NaeMZ4bVJAm6vq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.551345\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160824233254Yj1OmvDtik89yd4x.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.733496\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160824233254GKENPq5Rfdz0SVIm.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.646699\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160824233255GRtApFYhqQWrS3lI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.860636\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160824233255HqSxyjgtauhJdRX9.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.646699\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Conbox by JiyounKim Studio</h3><p>当炎热的夏日“烧烤模式”结束，尽职的电扇们也到了需要“退居幕后”的时候。然而储存电扇往往要占据不小的空间，与它们一年中短暂的“上岗”时间相比就显得有些浪费。为了提升空间利用率，韩国工作室 <a href=\"http://www.jiyounkim.com/project_html/project_conbox.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">JiyounKim Studio</a> 推出了这款名为 <a href=\"http://www.jiyounkim.com/project_html/project_conbox.html\" rel=\"nofollow\">Conbox</a> 的风扇，所有组件均可轻松拆卸。底座和风扇部分组合在一起后，中间的空隙还可以用来收纳两段式的风扇杆。目前这款产品还处于原型阶段，尚未投入生产。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160824233233PF7UamA49QR1wLGp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.589242\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160824233233u5AHjSO3sRUM0oYX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.607579\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160824233233oX50nI9VGr17pdTF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.627139\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160824233234KmJrsQ6ChUIElHB4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.503667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160824233234Vmvr97WtIZTXdshN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.566015\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160824233234fNlUBeLzypIqQ9HX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.674817\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Maburu and Porin by mob</h3><p>墨西哥设计工作室 <a href=\"http://mob.com.mx/en/\" rel=\"nofollow\">mob</a> 最近推出的两款大理石桌或许会改变你对这种材质的印象。圆桌 <a href=\"http://mob.com.mx/en/shop/maburu\" rel=\"nofollow\">Maburu</a> 的桌面从中间裂开，由黄铜件连接的两片“桌腿”就像是桌面的延伸，直角和圆形的搭配看起来也并不突兀。半圆形的 <a href=\"http://mob.com.mx/en/shop/porin\" rel=\"nofollow\">Porin</a> 有着异曲同工之妙，除了底部的黄铜件之外还利用一根贯穿桌面的木头作为支撑，木头的前端还特别做了烧制处理，让人感受到一股原始的美丽。你可以点击两款家具名字跳转至它们的购买链接。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160824232945aI7wKRbYmpDvAeNz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160824232945sr4aQJOWM0bIV3Rh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.664844\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160824232945NQy5Jku6SxwOacLZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160824232946Sufe2xa8TnMsVD4z.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160824232946nTdpNWQLwsqKbChZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Veiled Lady by Damien Gernay</h3><p>如果你觉得有着菌类植物造型的灯具并不稀奇的话，<a href=\"http://www.damiengernay.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Damien Gernay</a> 设计的这套 <a href=\"http://www.damiengernay.com/portfolio/veiled-lady/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Veiled Lady</a> 系列或许会让你大开眼界。Gernay 使用脱蜡法使铜液塑形成竹荪特有的细致网状裙构造，纤薄的灯罩看上去似乎会随风舞动一样。系列中包含了台灯、落地灯以及吊灯三种款式，由于每件灯具都采用手工定型，它们的造型也各不相同。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160824233104iascDbGzBQ6uop5t.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160824233103N3rkoRctwWUEalSV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160824233104v4bB6JEz2fP8nNMe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160824233105YSk3o0ZrqJ6WmTdU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160824233104HldVZQXGunD28hTj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160824233105ojEiA1ztsv4QP9CM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Leaf-band-aid by Ye Wenzai et al.</h3><p>你有没有忘记将创可贴从伤口上取下的经历？为了提醒人们按时更换创可贴，来自中国的设计团队以过去人们用叶子掩盖伤口加速愈合过程为灵感，推出了一款树叶造型的创可贴 Leaf-band-aid。它由一种特殊的变色材质制成，在感应到人体温度之后会随着时间流逝由绿色转变为黄色，就像是树叶变枯一样，非常讨巧。作为一款既有趣又实用的概念设计，它此前还获得了 <a href=\"http://www.red-dot.sg/en/online-exhibition/leaf-band-aid/\" rel=\"nofollow\">2015 年红点奖</a>的肯定。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160824233147s8LXfMimx6uQTo94.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160824233125gDwzMeYfK9An7iqL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160824233125c4jagOI7ervsAFKJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160824233125RmAdTQiWj2LeFrsq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Alpaca Loca by Lindsey Nelson</h3><p>用羊驼毛制成的各种颜色鲜艳的织物是一种秘鲁当地常见的纪念品，在美国设计师 <a href=\"http://www.lindseynelsondesigns.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Lindsey Nelson</a> 看来，没有比羊驼这种可爱的动物本身更直观的包装元素了。<a href=\"http://www.lindseynelsondesigns.com/alpaca-loca-1/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Alpaca Loca</a> 就是她所设计的一款概念包装，两片木板分别表现了羊驼的正面和背面，身体的部分则是一根圆管，用来放置卷起来的织物。三个部分组合在一起就变成了一只木羊驼，取出纪念品之后也可以作为一件小玩具或是装饰品。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160824233206CMo9LOtS40r2wQ3d.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667143\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160824233206YteizdKgLH87hIf0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667143\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201608242332062JcNb6C9BI7TulsY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667143\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160824233206QIFZh91cf5VYkzxT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160824233207L9iGZskSfJehyNQ8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667143\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}